{"type": "article", "id": 17647, "title": "布丁包装", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-17T06:50:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 23, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606155845oNB72bCshDzUjyI9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tNaughty But Rice 是一个新的英国食品品牌，专做大米布丁（rice pudding），他们邀请英国设计师 Robot Food 做了包装设计。有红色、橙色和棕色三种，上面用方块、半圆等图案代表了具体的食物指向，都有点像儿童画。简单的线条和明亮的色彩显得单纯干净，同时能见到波点、条纹等时尚元素，非常活泼。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144742ejsAyiMUE3Bun6m0.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"405\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7527881\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144743dsvhUtGo24ZFXVJr.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"336\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62453532\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144743JB1dUwuXKVsgqylL.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"391\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.7267658\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261447440igRh8I1lpwWQF79.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"336\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62453532\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144745G6FYw7iCnfTVlXpy.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"430\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.79925651\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144746GtbciWB2hRQjXFpT.jpg\" width=\"538\" height=\"336\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.62453532\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}